To all Convoso-ians!

This is our fork of the github.com/cmusphinx/pocketsphinx package.  It is set up so that we can, via the github.com UI, sync the default branch of that repo to ours, but it does so manually.

Please follow typical repo patterns:   Fork your feature branches for dev work off of staging.  Then the merge process, after PR, would be feature branch -> staging -> candidate -> main.

Once changes are in main, if you feel that they are pertinent for the cmusphinx project, please check with superiors if necessay in order to submit a PR back to cmusphinx/pocketsphinx for potential inclusion.

